n the interior vesicle surface,\n$\\boldsymbol{n}$ is the unit normal vector of the vesicle boundary, $K_\\perp$\nis the membrane permeability, $\\eta_e$ is the viscosity of the solvent, and\n$\\ell_m$ is the membrane thickness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Dec 2021 02:53:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 May 2022 03:53:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 May 2022 15:22:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-24"}
